Be careful with this one, there is definitely inputs that will produce infinite loops.<br>
inputs have to be ! or 'space' to meet the ternary input requirement.<br>
example:<br>
inp:`!  ! !`<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;:`// !/`<br>
out:`!:/!  ! !`<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;`\// !/`<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;`!  ! !`<br>
